---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /europe/index.html
title: Tech Event Tracker — Europe
pageType: europe
---
<h1>Europe</h1>
<p>Upcoming on-site technology events across Europe (excluding the Netherlands), soonest first.</p>

{% set list = collections.europe | upcomingByDate %}
{% if list.length === 0 %}
<p><em>No upcoming Europe events tracked yet.</em></p>
{% else %}
<ul class="event-list">
{% for e in list %}
  <li>
    <div class="event-title"><a href="{{ e.url | absUrl }}">{{ e.data.title }}</a></div>
    <div class="event-meta">
      <time datetime="{{ e.data.eventDate | isoDate }}">{{ e.data.eventDate | eventDate }}</time>
      {%- if e.data.location %} &middot; {{ e.data.location }}{% endif -%}
    </div>
    {%- if e.data.description %}<p class="event-desc">{{ e.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
    <p class="event-links">
      {%- if e.data.website %}<a href="{{ e.data.website }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Official site &rarr;</a>{% endif -%}
      {%- if e.data.tickets %} <a href="{{ e.data.tickets }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tickets &rarr;</a>{% endif -%}
    </p>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% endif %}
